  "recipeInstructions": "1. Soften the cream cheese.\n2. Place all ingredients (except crab) in a pot and heat until simmering, about 15 minutes.\n3. Stir in the softened cream cheese.\n4. Turn off the heat and carefully fold in the crab meat.",
